  "description_snippet": "COMPONENT  \nwebrtc  \ncomponent:Blink>WebRTC   \ncomponents:Blink>WebRTC   \n  \n**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nRtcEventLogEncoderLegacy::EncodeRtcpPacket allocates a stack buffer of size IP_PACKET_SIZE(1500) however real packets may be up to 2048.  \nResults in stack-buffer-overflow WRITE.  \n  \n**VERSION*"
